      <p style="font-style:normal; margin-bottom:14px;">Contractors need coverage that survives a GC's certificate review — right limits, right endorsements, right additional insured language. We work with markets that actually write contractors, including roofing, excavation, and specialty trades that standard carriers won't touch.</p>
      <div style="display:flex; gap:10px; flex-wrap:wrap;">
