      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="testimonial" style="margin-bottom:48px; border-left:3px solid var(--terracotta);">
      <h3 style="margin-bottom:12px;">👥 Workers' Compensation</h3>
      <p style="font-style:normal; margin-bottom:14px;">Required by Arizona law once you have employees. We rate it to your actual payroll and job classifications — not an estimate that blows up at audit. We also help you understand the experience modification factor and how to keep your rate competitive over time.</p>
      <div style="display:flex; gap:10px; flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <span style="font-size:0.8rem; background:var(--sand); padding:6px 12px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:600;">All-state filing</span>
        <span style="font-size:0.8rem; background:var(--sand); padding:6px 12px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:600;">Payroll-rated</span>
        <span style="font-size:0.8rem; background:var(--sand); padding:6px 12px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:600;">Audit support</span>
