    <div class="testimonial" style="margin-bottom:48px; border-left:3px solid var(--terracotta);">
      <h3 style="margin-bottom:12px;">🚚 Commercial Auto</h3>
      <p style="font-style:normal; margin-bottom:14px;">Personal auto policies exclude business use. If your team drives to job sites, delivers product, or uses vehicles as part of operations, you need commercial auto — and we can cover everything from a single work truck to a multi-vehicle fleet under one program.</p>
      <div style="display:flex; gap:10px; flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <span style="font-size:0.8rem; background:var(--sand); padding:6px 12px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:600;">Fleet programs</span>
        <span style="font-size:0.8rem; background:var(--sand); padding:6px 12px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:600;">Hired & non-owned</span>
        <span style="font-size:0.8rem; background:var(--sand); padding:6px 12px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:600;">Physical damage</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="testimonial" style="border-left:3px solid var(--terracotta);">
      <h3 style="margin-bottom:12px;">🏗️ Builder's Risk</h3>
      <p style="font-style:normal; margin-bottom:14px;">Covers a structure under construction against fire, theft, and weather damage — from ground-break to certificate of occupancy. We write both single-project and blanket builder's risk policies depending on your volume.</p>
      <div style="display:flex; gap:10px; flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <span style="font-size:0.8rem; background:var(--sand); padding:6px 12px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:600;">Single-project</span>
        <span style="font-size:0.8rem; background:var(--sand); padding:6px 12px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:600;">Blanket programs</span>
        <span style="font-size:0.8rem; background:var(--sand); padding:6px 12px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:600;">Materials in transit</span>
